Himachal Corona Daily Report: 14 June (9 PM report)

16 new positive cases of Covid-19 and 17 recoveries were reported in #HimachalPradesh today. Total cases in the hill-State stands at 518 including 326 recoveries and 6 fatalities.

#COVID19India #CoronaUpdatesInIndia  #Covid_19 https://t.co/c06Pq6RBxV
